{"type":"message","id":"4baaaf7e","parentId":"6f708b1c","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:21:51.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Read the file `~/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/aigc-short-drama-tutorial.md`\n2. Make it visual/presentable\n3. Send it to them\n\nLet me first read the file to understand its contents, then present it in a nice format.","thinkingSignature":"ea3f9d01564ce050de63dd1633348c77cff75299d4ae0b2a4b16a50ade6af145"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_4w86fq9koszm_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/hochoy/.openclaw/workspace-comedy/aigc-short-drama-tutorial.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90,"output":109,"cacheRead":24848,"cacheWrite":28782,"totalTokens":53829,"cost":{"input":0.000027,"output":0.00013079999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0007454399999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0034538399999999997,"total":0.004357079999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774344102597}}
{"type":"message","id":"703194ac","parentId":"4baaaf7e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:21:51.563Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4w86fq9koszm_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# AIGC微短剧制作教程\n\n## 一、制作流程\n\n### 1. 选题策划\n- 热门题材：甜宠、逆袭、悬疑、古装、职场\n- 公式：强冲突 + 高共鸣 + 快节奏 + 悬念钩子\n\n### 2. 剧本创作（3分钟结构）\n```\n0:00-0:10  钩子：冲突爆发\n0:10-0:40  铺垫：背景介绍\n0:40-1:30  发展：矛盾升级\n1:30-2:20  高潮：最大冲突\n2:20-2:50  结局：留悬念\n2:50-3:00  CTA：引导关注\n```\n\n### 3. 角色设计\n- Midjourney生成角色定装照\n- 使用--seed或--cref保持角色一致性\n\n### 4. 分镜脚本\n| 镜号 | 时间 | 景别 | 画面 | 配音 |\n|------|------|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 0-5s | 特写 | 女主震惊 | 惊呼声 |\n\n### 5. 画面生成\n- 工具：Midjourney/SD/即梦/可灵\n- 流程：角色定装照 → 场景图 → 分镜画面\n\n### 6. 配音制作\n- 工具：MiniMax/ElevenLabs/Edge TTS\n- 用Whisper生成时间戳字幕\n\n### 7. 音乐音效\n- 音乐：Suno/Udio/剪映\n- 音效：freesound/爱给网\n\n### 8. 视频合成（剪映）\n1. 导入素材\n2. 排列图片\n3. 添加转场\n4. 添加字幕\n5. 调整时长匹配配音\n6. 添加音乐音效\n7. 调色\n8. 导出（1080×1920, 30fps）\n\n## 二、工具推荐\n\n| 环节 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| 剧本 | ChatGPT/Claude/Kimi |\n| 角色 | Midjourney/SD/即梦 |\n| 画面 | MJ/SD/可灵/Runway |\n| 配音 | MiniMax/ElevenLabs |\n| 音乐 | Suno/Udio/剪映 |\n| 合成 | 剪映/PR/Remotion |\n\n## 三、关键技巧\n\n1. **角色一致性**：固定seed或用--cref\n2. **节奏把控**：每30秒一个反转\n3. **开头3秒**：必须有冲突或悬念\n4. **字幕同步**：用Whisper生成真实时间戳\n5. **音量平衡**：配音 > 音乐"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774344111561}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e82b94b","parentId":"703194ac","timestamp":"2026-03-24T09:22:14.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to make this content more visually appealing and presentable. The user is in Feishu, so I should format this nicely. Since they asked me to \"可视化之后发给我\", I'll read the file, make it visually nice, and then send it via the feishu message tool.\n\nLet me format this as a nicely structured message and send it to the user via feishu. Since this is in a 1:1 chat with me (the main agent), I should use message to send to the sender.\n\nActually, looking at the inbound context, this is a direct message from ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352 to me (main agent). So I can reply directly here.\n\nWait, actually the user is asking me to make the content \"visual\" and send it to them. I should create a nicely formatted message. Since I'm in a feishu channel, I should use the message tool to send to them, or just reply normally with the formatted content.\n\nLet me just reply with a nicely formatted version of the content in my response, since that's the most direct way. Or I could use the message tool to send it as a formatted message.\n\nLet me use the message tool to send a nicely formatted version since the user specifically asked me to \"发给我\" (send it to me), implying they want it delivered as a message.","thinkingSignature":"2405794134abd064feefbb3faf9be342f75d330d626d86bcad8eabf8cfe5e16d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ecxall7yh2fu_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","target":"user:ou_a40d252df8eedac11a6ca82ca1b65352","message":"📺 **AIGC微短剧制作教程**\n\n---\n\n**一、制作流程**\n\n**1. 选题策划**\n• 热门题材：甜宠、逆袭、悬疑、古装、职场\n• 公式：强冲突 + 高共鸣 + 快节奏 + 悬念钩子\n\n**2. 剧本创作（3分钟结构）**\n```\n⏱ 0:00-0:10  钩子：冲突爆发\n⏱ 0:10-0:40  铺垫：背景介绍\n⏱ 0:40-1:30  发展：矛盾升级\n⏱ 1:30-2:20  高潮：最大冲突\n⏱ 2:20-2:50  结局：留悬念\n⏱ 2:50-3:00  CTA：引导关注\n```\n\n**3. 角色设计**\n• Midjourney 生成角色定装照\n• 使用 --seed 或 --cref 保持角色一致性\n\n**4. 分镜脚本**\n| 镜号 | 时间 | 景别 | 画面 | 配音 |\n|------|------|------|------|------|\n| 1 | 0-5s | 特写 | 女主震惊 | 惊呼声 |\n\n**5. 画面生成**\n• 工具：Midjourney / SD / 即梦 / 可灵\n• 流程：角色定装照 → 场景图 → 分镜画面\n\n**6. 配音制作**\n• 工具：MiniMax / ElevenLabs / Edge TTS\n• 用 Whisper 生成时间戳字幕\n\n**7. 音乐音效**\n• 音乐：Suno / Udio / 剪映\n• 音效：freesound / 爱给网\n\n**8. 视频合成（剪映）**\n```\n1️⃣ 导入素材\n2️⃣ 排列图片\n3️⃣ 添加转场\n4️⃣ 添加字幕\n5️⃣ 调整时长匹配配音\n6️⃣ 添加音乐音效\n7️⃣ 调色\n8️⃣ 导出（1080×1920, 30fps）\n```\n\n---\n\n**二、工具推荐**\n\n| 环节 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| 🎬 剧本 | ChatGPT / Claude / Kimi |\n| 👤 角色 | Midjourney / SD / 即梦 |\n| 🖼️ 画面 | MJ / SD / 可灵 / Runway |\n| 🎙️ 配音 | MiniMax / ElevenLabs |\n| 🎵 音乐 | Suno / Udio / 剪映 |\n| ✂️ 合成 | 剪映 / PR / Remotion |\n\n---\n\n**三、关键技巧**\n\n✅ **角色一致性** — 固定 seed 或用 --cref\n✅ **节奏把控** — 每30秒一个反转\n✅ **开头3秒** — 必须有冲突或悬念\n✅ **字幕同步** — 用 Whisper 生成真实时间戳\n✅ **音量平衡** — 配音 > 音乐\n\n---\n\n*教程来源：AIGC微短剧制作教程*"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36062,"output":1011,"cacheRead":18359,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55432,"cost":{"input":0.0108186,"output":0.0012132,"cacheRead":0.0005507699999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012582569999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774344111564}}
